20 educational excellence scholarship and supplemental award, or a supplemental
21 award only, an eligible high school or postsecondary student shall:
22 (a) Enroll in and attend a participating institution as a full-time student or a part-
23 time student; and
24 (b) Maintain eligibility as provided in subsection (3) of this section.
